nsparent; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">，<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">被静态修饰的成员，可以直接被类名所调用。</strong>也就是说，静态的成员多了一种调用方式。<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">类名.静态方式</strong>。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">，<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">静态随着类的加载而加载，而且优先于对象存在。</strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">弊端：</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">，有些数据是对象特有的数据，是不可以被静态修饰的。因为那样的话，特有数据会变成对象的共享数据。这样对事物的描述就出了问题。所以，在定义静态时，必须要明确，这个数据是否是被对象所共享的。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">2</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">，<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">静态方法只能访问静态成员，不可以访问非静态成员。</strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">因为静态方法加载时，优先于对象存在，所以没有办法访问对象中的成员。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">3</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">，<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: red;\">静态方法中不能使用this，super关键字。</span></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-f