 inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体; color: red;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">成员变量和静态变量的区别：</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">1</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">，成员变量所属于对象，所以也称为实例变量。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">静态变量所属于类，所以也称为类变量。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun