9;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">多重继承的出现，就有了继承体系。体系中的顶层父类是通过不断向上抽取而来的。它里面定义的该体系最基本最共性内容的功能。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">所以，一个体系要想被使用，直接查阅该系统中的父类的功能即可知道该体系的基本用法。那么想要使用一个体系时，需要建立对象。建议建立最子类对象，因为最子类不仅可以使用父类中的功能。还可以使用子类特有的一些功能。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体; color: red;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">简单说：对于一个继承体系的使用，查阅顶层父类中的内容，创建最底层子类的对象。</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体; color: red;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">子父类出现后，类中的成员都有了哪些特点：</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">1</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">：成员变量。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">当子父类中出现一样的属性时，子类类型的对象，调用该属性，值是子类的属性值。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">如果想要调用父类中的属性值，需要使用一个关键字：<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: red;\">super</span></strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: red;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">This</strong></span></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">：</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">代表是本类类型的对象引用。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: red;\">Super</span></span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">：</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">代表是子类所属的父类中的内存空间引用。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">注意：子父类中通常是不会出现同名成员变量的，因为父类中只要定义了，子类就不用在定义了，直接继承过来用就可以了。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">2</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">：成员函数。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">当子父类中出现了一模一样的方法时，建立子类对象会运行子类中的方法。好像父类中的方法被覆盖掉一样。所以这种情况，是函数的另一个特性：<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: red;\">覆盖</span>(复写，重写)</strong></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">什么时候使用覆盖呢？当一个类的功能内容需要修改时，可以通过覆盖来实现。</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">3</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">：构造函数。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">发现子类构造函数运行时，先运行了父类的构造函数。为什么呢?</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">原因：<span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: red;\">子类的<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">所有构造函数中的第一行</strong>，其实都有一条隐身的语句super();</span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">super():&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\">表示父类的构造函数，并会调用于参数相对应的父类中的构造函数。而super():是在调用父类中空参数的构造函数。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">为什么子类对象初始化时，都需要调用父类中的函数？(为什么要在子类构造函数的第一行加入这个super()?)</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">因为子类继承父类，会继承到父类中的数据，所以必须要看父类是如何对自己的数据进行初始化的。所以子类在进行对象初始化时，先调用父类的构造函数，这就是<strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">子类的实例化过程</strong>。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体; color: red;\">注意：</span></strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体; color: blue;\">子类中所有的构造函数都会默认访问父类中的空参数的构造函数，因为每一个子类构造内第一行都有默认的语句super();</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体; color: blue;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">如果父类中没有空参数的构造函数，那么子类的构造函数内，必须通过super语句指定要访问的父类中的构造函数。</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体; color: blue;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">如果子类构造函数中用this来指定调用子类自己的构造函数，那么被调用的构造函数也一样会访问父类中的构造函数。</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(61, 70, 77); font-family: &#39;Pingfang SC&#39;, STHeiti, &#39;Lantinghei SC&#39;, &#39;Open Sans&#39;, Arial, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, &#39;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&#39;, SimSun, sans-serif; line-height: 28px; background-color: rgb(248, 248, 248);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: small;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px; white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight